391
00:20:04,035 --> 00:20:06,169
Por favor, mande a Caitlin entrar agora.

392
00:20:06,204 --> 00:20:07,270
Caitlin?

393
00:20:07,305 --> 00:20:08,638
E nós?

394
00:20:08,672 --> 00:20:10,774
